{"tid":1485794,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日有份淋雨嘅人入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-08-18T16:42:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T17:09:00.000Z","uid":158524,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"327ae58fa94d3aafd735fa69c73cbba539f57b44","tid":1485794,"uid":158524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:42:46.000Z","msg":"首先 好多謝你地 放棄自己寶貴嘅一日出嚟淋雨 <br />\n我地制造左一次又一次嘅記錄<br />\n但請 唔好因此而太過開心<br />\n我地五大訴求 一個都未達到<br />\n<br />\n再者 唔好再互相屌嚟屌去 互相捉鬼 好唔好？<br />\n唔想再變成雨革2.0嘅<br />\n請記得 <span style=\"font-size: large;\">不分化 不割席</span><br />\n我明白 有時候 大家每次都想出全力 <br />\n但喺 欲速則不達<br />\n<br />\n仲有我想求大家 繼續改變身邊同自己唔同意見嘅人<br />\n政治 唔係要一個人去認同你<br />\n政治 喺要令身邊意見分歧嘅人 思想上有改變而認同你<br />\n<br />\n最後我地點都好 唔好唔記得黑警做過乜 永遠都要追究佢地班仆街 <br />\n仲有香港人應承我 要永遠記得 嗰6位烈士 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"8fd780f758ec2bb23cab7acc265d43e021ca0297","tid":1485794,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:43:54.000Z","msg":"推！！"},{"pid":"69a2072304e63f73d54f04b50f3f29c1356d2834","tid":1485794,"uid":158524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:43:55.000Z","msg":"希望你地唔好善忘"},{"pid":"970de38a322b1ede6e32ed7179ed626ab75c4070","tid":1485794,"uid":158524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:44:35.000Z","msg":"大家都係香港人 大家都係兄弟姊妹 大家係共患難"},{"pid":"1a59b8f9e01f92591c9cfab8b6bf14b684f8a0f6","tid":1485794,"uid":266683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:44:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tdQBybb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtdQBybb.jpg&h=abca2eb5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d633aabb5f091138c703778d96061dbb055c6fbe","tid":1485794,"uid":158524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:45:33.000Z","m